[Unfortunately, this report only states where the patient was hospitalised, the Nork Hospital in Yerevan, located at: http://www.fallingrain.com/world/AM/11/Nork.html. Where the patient was infected is not stated. Yerevan is a distance from Lori and Sirak, where the previous cases were, close to the northwest border.

For a map of Armenia showing Lori and Sirak, go to: http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/commonwealth/armenia_physio-2002.jpg. For the site of the village of Artagyuh, see the OIE report via ProMED-mail archived post 20131024.2019231. - Mod.MHJ

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/1HT_.]
